<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10476487>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Amynthas antoanensis sp. nov., holotype. A, G: Male pore region, ventral view (mp = male pore; gm = gential markings); B, I: Spermathecal region (sp = spermathecal pore; gm = gential markings); C, D: Spermathecae (amp = ampulla; dv = diverticula); E, H: Intestinal caeca; F: Prostatic gland. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10476487/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

